title: 12/15/20 DPS-BEST OF
itunes:title: 12/15/20 DPS-BEST OF
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP Recaps last night's shootout between the Browns and Ravens. What positives can Cleveland take away from the loss? He also discusses the College Football Playoff Rankings. Under which scenario could we see Clemson not make the Final Four? We're joined by Browns beat writer for the Plain Dealer Mary Kay Cabot, ESPN Monday Night Football analyst Louis Riddick, and Yahoo sports columnist Dan Wetzel.
